cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.DS

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with Reinforcement Learning (RL) and value functions. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as RL is a subfield of AI. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics) as RL is commonly used in robotics. It could also be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as RL is used in control systems. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as it presents a new approach for optimistic initialization.
